            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "My motivation was three fold\n\n1. After the new intro we inevitably had people asking how to change it back/override it. This gives that entry point\n\n2. You made a comment about google-esque Easter eggs etc in the logo. This would make that easier\nSide note: Assuming this was in the logo people could 'opt-in' by using the built in logo 'component'\n\n3. Once I started doing it then over ride point felt quite 'neovimmy'.",
